#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:9
msgid ""
"Bugfix: Role list page now shows only current tenant's roles (previously "
"showed all tenants)"
msgstr "修复：角色列表页仅显示当前租户的角色（此前会显示所有租户）"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:10
msgid ""
"Bugfix: Workflow design page: fix issue where role could not be selected "
"as assignee"
msgstr "修复：工作流设计页面无法将角色指定为审批人的问题"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:11
msgid "Improvement: Add detailed user guide for MCP configuration"
msgstr "优化：为 MCP 功能增加详细使用指南"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:16
msgid "r3.2.0"
msgstr "r3.2.0"

