msgid "Feature: add Microsoft OIDC and wecom QR scan login"
msgstr "功能：新增 Microsoft OIDC 与企业微信扫码登录"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:30
msgid "Feature: add file&rich text&external data field"
msgstr "功能：新增文件、富文本与外部数据字段"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:31
msgid "Feature: add workflow design auto layout feature"
msgstr "功能：工作流设计支持自动布局"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:32
msgid "Security: security issues fix"
msgstr "安全：安全问题修复"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:37
msgid "r3.0.1"
msgstr "r3.0.1"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:38
msgid ""
"Docker Compose: custom Redis/Postgres ports, drop version key, ARM build,"
" pinned tags."
msgstr "Docker Compose：支持自定义 Redis/Postgres 端口，移除 version 字段，提供 ARM 构建，镜像标签固定。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:39
msgid ""
"User-facing: reset personal password; choose workflow version on create; "
"English publish hint; flow preview node text; default language follows "
"browser."
msgstr "用户侧：可重置个人密码；创建流程时可选版本；英文发布提示；流程预览节点文案；默认语言跟随浏览器。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:40
msgid ""
"Frontend: remove unused imports; upgrade yarn 4 / Node 22 / TS 5; "
"incremental `yarn tsc`; type fixes; required label handled."
msgstr "前端：清理未使用 import；升级到 yarn 4 / Node 22 / TS5 ；类型修复；必填标签处理。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:41
msgid ""
"I18n: numbers/dates/components/templates covered; i18-ally config; "
"default language follows browser."
msgstr "国际化：覆盖数字/日期/组件/模板；补充 i18-ally 配置；默认语言跟随浏览器。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:42
msgid ""
"Quality (workflow/forms): workflow version type editable; ticket field "
"edits fixed; edge required check; user component drag fixed; rule editor "
"i18n; notification editing fixed."
msgstr "质量（流程/表单）：流程版本类型可编辑；工单字段修改已修复；连线必填校验；用户组件拖拽修复；规则编辑器国际化；通知编辑修复。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:43
msgid ""
"Quality (templates/dates): date/time placeholders fixed; title template "
"parsing fixed (creator, select display, editing)."
msgstr "质量（模板/时间）：修复日期/时间占位符；修复标题模板解析（创建人、下拉展示、编辑）。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:44
msgid "Ops: stdout logging restored; add initial user on deploy."
msgstr "运维：恢复 stdout 日志输出；部署时新增初始用户。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.1+.rst:45
msgid "Docs: issue templates refreshed; user/API docs."
msgstr "文档：更新 issue 模板；完成用户/API 文档。"

